These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, pumpkin
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | cauliflower   | pumpkin   |
| Transport   | helicopter | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | tea | milk   |
| Sport      | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, peas
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, punk
1. the person eating orange is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peas | orange |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | punk     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, plum
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | plum | cabbage |
| Pet    | hedgehog    | rat |

